%% OSPP Online Session Flow (Most Common Path)
%% Reference: spec/04-flows.md, Section 3; examples/flows/02-online-session.md

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor User as 📱 Mobile App
    participant Server as 🖥️ Server
    participant Broker as 📡 MQTT Broker
    participant Station as ⚙️ Station

    Note over User,Station: Prerequisites: Station booted, bays Available, user authenticated

    %% Session initiation
    User->>Server: POST /sessions (bayId, serviceId, durationSeconds)
    Server->>Server: Verify credits/payment
    Server-->>User: 201 Created (sessionId, status: "Pending")

    %% StartService via MQTT
    Server->>Broker: PUBLISH ospp/v1/stations/{station_id}/to-station
    Broker->>Station: StartService REQUEST [MSG-005]
    Station->>Station: Validate bay, activate hardware
    Station-->>Broker: StartService RESPONSE (Accepted)
    Broker-->>Server: PUBLISH ospp/v1/stations/{station_id}/to-server
    Server-->>User: Push notification: "Session started"

    %% Bay status change
    Station->>Broker: StatusNotification EVENT (Occupied)
    Broker->>Server: StatusNotification [MSG-009]

    %% Meter values (periodic)
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Station,Server: Every MeterValuesInterval (default 15s)
        Station->>Broker: MeterValues EVENT [MSG-010]
        Broker->>Server: MeterValues (liquidMl, consumableMl, energyWh)
        Server-->>User: Real-time usage update
    end

    %% Session stop
    User->>Server: POST /sessions/{id}/stop
    Server->>Broker: PUBLISH StopService REQUEST [MSG-006]
    Broker->>Station: StopService REQUEST
    Station->>Station: Deactivate hardware, calculate final values
    Station-->>Broker: StopService RESPONSE (Accepted, meterValues, creditsCharged)
    Broker-->>Server: StopService RESPONSE

    %% Finishing → Available
    Station->>Broker: StatusNotification EVENT (Finishing)
    Broker->>Server: StatusNotification [MSG-009]

    Station->>Broker: StatusNotification EVENT (Available)
    Broker->>Server: StatusNotification [MSG-009]

    %% Final billing
    Server->>Server: Calculate final cost, refund unused credits
    Server-->>User: Push notification: "Session complete" + receipt

    Note over User,Station: Bay returns to Available, ready for next session
